		"description": "<p>Use this method to set the score of the specified user in a game message. On success, if the message is not an inline message, the <a href=\"/docs/api/types/Message\">Message</a> is returned, otherwise <em>True</em> is returned. Returns an error, if the new score is not greater than the user's current score in the chat and <em>force</em> is <em>False</em>.</p>",
