		"description": "<p>This <a href=\"https://core.telegram.org/bots/api/#available-types\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">object</a> represents an incoming update.<br>At most <strong>one</strong> of the optional fields can be present in any given update.</p>",
