		"description": "<p>This object defines the criteria used to request suitable users. Information about the selected users will be shared with the bot when the corresponding button is pressed. <a href=\"https://core.telegram.org/bots/features#chat-and-user-selection\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">More about requesting users »</a></p>",
